casebody.data:
Jennie Chiseri, Respondent, v Common Council of the City of Peekskill, Appellant. Decided April 7, 1977

Reported below, 54 AD2d 705.

Appeal dismissed, without costs, by the Court of Appeals sua spon te, upon the ground that the question certified does not present a question of law decisive of the correctness of the determination of the Appellate Division (see Barclay’s Ice Cream Co. v Local No. 757 of Ice Cream Drivers & Employees Union, 41 NY2d 269, 273).
